column12: Call your driver when all passengers have collected luggage and are ready to depart. Proceed to baggage claim #16. There is a 5-10 minute wait for your shuttle to arrive once driver has been called. If you do not have driver name & number call dispatch at (206) 233-9233. You may also dial 55 from any courtesy phone to speak with airport customer service. Let them know you are waiting for your chartered shuttle.

column12: Call your driver when all passengers have collected luggage and are ready to depart. Proceed to baggage claim #16. Take escalator, stairs or elevator to skybridge #6 and cross to parking garage. Take the BLUE elevators to Level One and follow the signs to holding area for cruise ships and charter buses. There is a 5-10 minute wait for your shuttle to arrive once driver has been called. If you do not have driver name & number call dispatch at (206) 233-9233. You may also dial 55 from any courtesy phone to speak with airport customer service. Let them know you are waiting for your chartered shuttle.
